sequenceDiagram
  participant Client
  participant Gateway
  participant ProductService
  participant ProductRepo

  Client->>Gateway: GET /api/products
  Gateway->>ProductService: GET /api/products
  ProductService->>ProductRepo: findAll()
  ProductRepo-->>ProductService: Flux<Product> (20 seeded)
  ProductService-->>Gateway: 200 OK [products]
  Gateway-->>Client: 200 OK [products]
